text: FC Dornbirn 1913 is an Austrian association football club from Dornbirn, Vorarlberg. They play in the 2. Liga, the 2nd level of Austrian football. The club was founded on March 12th, 1913. The homeground is the Birkenwiese stadium. They played four seasons in the top level league of Austrian football. ==Leagues (in brackets level)== *1960-61 Staatsliga (1) *1961-63 Regionalliga West (2) *1963-64 Staatsliga (1) *1964-69 Regionalliga West (2) *1969-70 Nationalliga (1) *1970- 74 Regionalliga West (2) *1974-75 Nationalliga (1) *1975-79 2.
